Generated Narrative: StructureDefinition BeModeleBirthReport

NameFlagsCard.TypeDescription & Constraints
BeModeleBirthReport 0..*BaseeBirth Report logical model
identifier 1..1IdentifierUnique identifier for the eBirth report
businessIdentifier 0..*IdentifierBusiness identifier for the eBirth report
recordedDate 1..1dateTimeDate and time when the eBirth report was recorded or last update.
observationPeriod 1..1PeriodPeriod during which the eBirth report is valid or applicable.
encounter 0..*Reference(Encounter)Transfer to another service?????????? What is this???? Why many??
patient 1..1Reference(Patient)The patient associated with the eBirth report.
recorder 1..1Reference(Practitioner)The practitioner who recorded the eBirth report.
interpreter 0..*Reference(Practitioner)The practitioner who interpreted the eBirth report.
status 1..1CodeableConceptThe status of the eBirth report, e.g., 'final', 'amended', 'cancelled'.
category 1..*CodeableConceptThe category of the eBirth report.
code 1..1CodeableConceptThe code of the eBirth report.
observationsAtBirth 0..*Reference(Observation)Observations made at the time of birth.
birthComplications 0..*Reference(Observation)Observations related to complications during birth.
note 0..*AnnotationNotes or comments related to the eBirth report.
document 0..1AttachmentPDF representation of the report
